#. Tag: title
#: locate.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Locate &GUI; Frontend"
msgstr "Poiščite &GUI; Frontend"

#. Tag: primary
#: locate.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Locate"
msgstr "Poišči"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krusader; has a &GUI; front end for the <command>locate</command> command "
"(findutils). Locate is used for fast file searching not from a folder but a "
"database. The package contains among other files, <command>locate</command> "
"and <command>updatedb</command>. <command>updatedb</command> goes through "
"the local file system and stores the file entries in the database. "
"<command>cron</command> often calls <command>updatedb</command> every night "
"(set with <application>KCron</application>). Choose <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Locate...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> "
"or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> to "
"start this feature. <link linkend=\"konfig-advanced\">Konfigurator</link> "
"can set additional arguments for <command>updatedb</command>."
msgstr ""
"&krusader; ima &GUI; sprednji del za ukaz <command>lociraj</command> "
"(findutils). Poišči se uporablja za hitro iskanje datotek ne iz mape, temveč "
"iz zbirke podatkov. Paket med drugimi datotekami vsebuje <command>locate</"
"command> in <command>updatedb</command>. <command>updatedb</command> gre "
"skozi lokalni datotečni sistem in shrani vnose datotek v bazo podatkov. "
"<command>cron</command> pogosto pokliče <command>updatedb</command> vsako "
"noč (nastavljeno z <application>KCron</application>). Izberite <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Poišči ...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> ali <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>L</keycap></"
"keycombo> za zagon te funkcije. <link linkend=\"konfig-advanced"
"\">Konfigurator</link> lahko nastavi dodatne argumente za <command>updatedb</"
"command>."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Checkbox Options"
msgstr "Možnosti potrditvenega polja"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show only the existing files</guilabel>: if the database contains "
"entries which no longer exist any more (deleted, moved since the last "
"<command>updatedb</command>), <command>locate</command> does not list them. "
"It checks the existence of each file before the listing in the results "
"window (slow)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prikaži samo obstoječe datoteke</guilabel>: če zbirka podatkov "
"vsebuje vnose, ki ne obstajajo več (izbrisani, premaknjeni od zadnjega "
"<command>updatedb</command>), <command>locate</command> naredi ne naštej "
"jih. Preveri obstoj vsake datoteke pred izpisom v oknu z rezultati (počasen)."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Case Sensitive</guilabel>: unchecking it allows lower and upper "
"case search."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Razlikuje med velikimi in malimi črkami</guilabel>: če počistite "
"polje, omogočite iskanje z malimi in velikimi črkami."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Action buttons"
msgstr "Akcijski gumbi"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Locate</guibutton>: executes <command>locate <replaceable>foo "
"foo</replaceable></command> and places its output into the results window."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Poišči</guibutton>: izvede <command>poišči <replaceable>foo foo</"
"replaceable></command> in postavi svoj rezultat v okno z rezultati."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Stop</guibutton>: stops the locating process."
msgstr "<guibutton>Ustavi</guibutton>: ustavi postopek lociranja."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>UpdateDB</guibutton>: starts <command>updatedb</command> for "
"updating the locate database after entering the root password."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>UpdateDB</guibutton>: zažene <command>updatedb</command> za "
"posodobitev locirane baze podatkov po vnosu korenskega gesla."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Close</guibutton>: closes the locate window."
msgstr "<guibutton>Zapri</guibutton>: zapre okno za iskanje."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "Results window"
msgstr "Okno z rezultati"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Double-click on an item: steps to its folder, makes the item visible and "
"closes the locate dialog."
msgstr ""
"Dvojni klik na element: pomakne se v njegovo mapo, naredi element viden in "
"zapre pogovorno okno za iskanje."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Right click: edits/views/finds the menu."
msgstr "Desni klik: uredi/pogleda/poišče meni."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F3</keycap>: views the current item."
msgstr "<keycap>F3</keycap>: ogled trenutnega elementa."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F4</keycap>: edits the current item."
msgstr "<keycap>F4</keycap>: uredi trenutni element."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>: finds files "
"in the results window."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>: poišče "
"datoteke v oknu z rezultati."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>: shows the "
"next search result."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>: prikaže "
"naslednji rezultat iskanja."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>: shows the "
"previous search result."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>: prikaže "
"prejšnji rezultat iskanja."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The results window supports dragging items to other windows and copy to "
"clipboard (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"Okno z rezultati podpira vlečenje elementov v druga okna in kopiranje v "
"odložišče (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>)."
